The ICC Academy Ground is a cricket ground located in Dubai Sports City, Dubai. ICC Academy provides state-of-the-art facilities with indoor and outdoor pitches, complemented by the latest technology to allow coaches to assess all areas of a playerâ€™s game. ICC Academy Oval 1 has hosted a total of 18 Twenty20 matches, of which 8 have been international matches. ICCA will be used for the 2014 ICC Under-19 Cricket World Cup. The two cricket grounds are installed with floodlights.


